FBIS4-43181 "drweu114_j_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY PDS Secretariat Resigns PDS Secretariat Resigns LD1306185394 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1834 GMT 13 Jun 94 LD1306185394 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] In the wake of Occhetto's decision to resign, the secretariat of the Democratic Party of the Left "obviously considers itself as having resigned," since "there is a bond of common responsibility," a communique said. It also said that the party's coordinating bureau is scheduled to meet at 1600 tomorrow.
